'''Agelmim n Mellaḥ''' d [[agelmam|agelmim]] amerɣan i d-yezga-n deg ugafa n ugezdu n [[Ṭṭaref]] (Lezzayer). Agelmim-a yezga-d ɣef yiri n [[Ilel Agrakal|Yilel Agrakal]] anda yebṭa gar-asen yiwen kan n usaka n [[ijdi|yijdi]] ayen yeǧǧan aman-is d [[amareɣ|imerɣanen]]
Agelmim-a d adeg anda ttekken waṭas n [[agṭiṭ|yigṭaṭ]] [[tinigt n iylalen|iminigen]] deg yinig-nsen gar [[Tafriqt|Tferka]] d Tuṛuft. Tajumma n ugelmim-a 860 km². Tudes ɣer-s yiwet n [[tagant|teẓgi]] n [[tayda|taydiwin]].

